ifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-1.fill.size_2000x1124.v1737996779.png" alt="iOS上一尘不染的屏幕截图" width="2000" height="1124" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-1.fill.size_800x450.v1737996779.png 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-1.fill.size_1400x787.v1737996779.png 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-1.fill.size_2000x1124.v1737996779.png 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">图片来源：Lindsey Ellefson</span></div></div><p>一尘不染<strong> </strong><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/spotless-a-simply-clean-home/id1067203863" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开" rel="noopener">iOS</a>和<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.launch27.spotlessvegas.wl&amp;hl=en_US&amp;gl=US" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开" rel="noopener">Android。</a></p><h2 id="if-you-need-reminders-clean-my-house">如果您需要提醒：打扫我的房子</h2><p>任务列表很棒（整个应用商店中都很丰富），但是如果您只是要避免打开您的应用以查看它们的人，那么这并不有用。清洁我的房子的设计旨在提醒您<em>一天</em>的清洁时间表应该是什么样的 - “不再担心每天早晨该做什么。”您可以控制每个通知弹出的频率；完成后，只需点击提醒即可打开应用并将其标记。请注意，它仅在Android上可用，并且在很大程度上得到广告的支持，广告底部底部且毫无意义。 </p><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-2.fill.size_2000x1124.v1737996779.png" alt="在Android上清洁我的房子" width="2000" height="1124" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-2.fill.size_800x449.v1737996779.png 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-2.fill.size_1400x787.v1737996779.png 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-2.fill.size_2000x1124.v1737996779.png 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">图片来源：贝丝·斯克瓦雷基（Beth Skwarecki）</span></div></div><p>清洁我的房子<strong> </strong><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.woohoosoftware.cleanmyhouse&amp;hl=en_GB" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开" rel="noopener">安卓。</a></p><h2 id="if-you-need-to-delegate-tody">如果您需要委派：Tody</h2><p>清洁不是一个人的工作，但是如果您使用的是只能看到的应用程序，那就感觉像这样。 <a href="https://todyapp.com/" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开" rel="noopener">Tody</a> Gamif gamif to calling和将整个家庭绳之以法。是的，它依赖于待办事项列表，就像此列表中的其他应用一样，但它还分配了用户之间的责任，并使用“级别”来轻松确定什么是紧迫的，什么不是，因此，您不会对需要做的事情感到不知所措。您需要一个高级帐户来访问设备和“聚焦任务”之间的数据同步的功能，该功能每年的价格为9.99美元，两人每年17.99美元，最多六人的价格为29.99美元。如果您想在该应用中添加12个人，则每年为59.99美元。即使在免费版本上，您也可以与一个名为“ Dusty”的小泥土竞争，以游戏化您的清洁月份。 </p><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-3.fill.size_2000x1127.v1737996779.png" alt="iOS上的tody应用" width="2000" height="1127" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-3.fill.size_800x451.v1737996779.png 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-3.fill.size_1400x789.v1737996779.png 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-3.fill.size_2000x1127.v1737996779.png 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">图片来源：Lindsey Ellefson</span></div></div><p> Tody可用<strong> </strong><a href="https://apps.apple.com/lv/app/tody/id595339588" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开" rel="noopener">iOS</a>和<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details/?id=com.looploop.tody&amp;hl=en_IN" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开" rel="noopener">Android。</a></p><h2 id="if-you-like-earning-points-do">如果您喜欢赚点：做</h2><p>一个让我们返回应用程序游戏的简单赚取系统的系统是什么？如果您是那种受到Snap或Duolingo Streaks激励的人，那么（以前做过）实际上可能会鼓励您打扫房屋。设定目标，每次完成首选的任务时，无论是清洁还是与生活方式有关，都会观看一个漂亮的小吧台充满颜色。您可以通过擦洗浴缸或每天喝足够的水来训练自己以获取那些甜蜜的点。您将获得7天的免费试用期，但是要获得无限的习惯，个性化您的目标并获得了发送给您的提醒，此后您需要每年支付59.99美元。 </p><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-5.fill.size_2000x1129.v1737996779.png" alt="在iOS上做应用" width="2000" height="1129" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-5.fill.size_800x451.v1737996779.png 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-5.fill.size_1400x790.v1737996779.png 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-5.fill.size_2000x1129.v1737996779.png 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">图片来源：Lindsey Ellefson</span></div></div><p> Do可以在<strong> </strong><a href="https://thedoneapp.com/" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开" rel="noopener">ios。</a></p><h2 id="bonus-tiktok">奖金：Tiktok</h2><p>如果您需要清洁灵感，那么清单可能不是路要走。根据真正激励您的原因，使用Tiktok可能会更好。该应用程序充满了<a href="https://www.lifehacker.com/15-of-the-best-cleantok-accounts-to-follow-on-tiktok-1849838334" target="">“清洁”的影响者，</a>他们分享了他们的顶级提示，以及真实的评论， <a href="https://www.lifehacker.com/8-cleaning-products-tiktok-absolutely-loves-1850095503" target="">产品建议</a>和<a href="https://www.lifehacker.com/10-of-the-best-and-worst-tiktok-cleaning-trends-of-20-1849888910" target="">黑客</a>。看到其他人使用技巧和窍门与他们的混乱和污垢作斗争非常奇怪，这会让您充满清洁的心情。 </p><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-6.fill.size_2000x1128.v1737996779.png" alt="Tiktok屏幕截图" width="2000" height="1128" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-6.fill.size_800x451.v1737996779.png 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-6.fill.size_1400x789.v1737996779.png 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2GQPKJ13F85DGMQEZWDK62/images-6.fill.size_2000x1128.v1737996779.png 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">图片来源：Lindsey Ellefson</span></div></div><p>由于联邦一级持续存在的问题，Tiktok无法下载，但是如果您是已经在手机上拥有它的1.7亿美国人之一，请尽可能获得清洁技巧。如果（何时？）它确实返回到应用商店，它将打开<strong> </strong><a href="https://apps.apple.com/ms/app/tiktok-videos-music-live/id835599320" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开" rel="noopener">iOS</a>和<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.zhiliaoapp.musically&amp;hl=en_US&amp;gl=US" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开" rel="noopener">Android。</a></p> ]]>;</content:encoded><link/> https://lifehacker.com/best-house-cleaning-apps?utm_medium=rss<dc:creator> Lindsey Ellefson</dc:creator><category><![CDATA[Cleaning & Organizing]]></category></item><item><title>我今天最喜欢的亚马逊交易：Microsoft Surface Pro</title><guid ispermalink="false"> 01JHNDSVN0RK2SZNT61PCYV3WS</guid><pubDate> Mon, 27 Jan 2025 16:00:00 +0000</pubDate><description> Microsoft Surface Pro 11是大学生最好的笔记本电脑之一。 </description><media:thumbnail url="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01JHNDSVN0RK2SZNT61PCYV3WS/hero-image.png"></media:thumbnail><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>我们可能会从此页面上的链接中获得佣金。出版后，交易定价和可用性可能会更改。</p><p> <a href="https://zdcs.link/aR32BE?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Microsoft%20Surface%20Pro%2011&amp;short_url=aR32BE&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">Microsoft Surface Pro 11</a>是一款